the eldest of the P<193><207><195>avas. The Yak<218>a asks 122 questions ç
and Yudhi<218><219>hira answers all of them satisfactorily.
After losing in the game of dice, the P<193><207><195>avas had to ç
live in a forest for twelve years. Once, during this period of banishment, ç
a br<193>hma<207>a complained to them that a deer had accidentally ç
carried away his ara<207>is (wooden pieces used for attrition to generate ç
