to pursue the animal and catch it or kill it but failed miserably. ç
When they were resting under a tree, tired and thirsty, Yudhi<218><219>hira ç
sent Nakula to fetch some drinking water. As he did not return even ç
after a long time, the other three brothers were also sent one by ç
one. When none of them turned up, Yudhi<218><219>hira himself went ç
in search of them. To his great astonishment and shock, he found all ç
